creator: Kreiz-Land Games
descriptionHtml:
Destruction simulation
Physically realistic simulator of destruction: release your stress, just chill out and destroy contractions!


Main features:
• Slow-motion
- You have the full control over the time rate: slow it down, increase the speed or just stop the simulation

• Guns
- Currently only lightning and explosions
But I plan to add much more!

• Maps
- 10 sandbox maps (more coming soon)
- Map editor: Still in development

• Campaign
- You got it right, complete challenges to unlock new weapons!

• Simulator
I have created this game for our personal needs - always dreamed of the game that allows you to destroy buildings, but there wasn't any, sooo... had to do one myself : )
descriptionShort: Destruction simulator: dimolish sandbox, realistic demolition physics simulation

Physically realistic simulator of destruction: release your stress, just chill out and destroy contractions, tear down buildings!


Main features:
• Slow-motion
- You have the full control over the time rate: slow it down, increase the speed or just stop the simulation

• Guns
- Missile
- Tornado
- Cascade grenade
- Lightning

• Maps
- 45 levels (more coming soon)
- Map editor

• Campaign
- You got it right, complete challenges and unlock new weapons!

• Sandbox
- Control time flow
- Just have fun with unlimited weaponry and destroy!

• Simulator
I have created this game for our personal needs - always dreamed of the game that allows you to destroy buildings, but there wasn't any, sooo... had to do one myself : )
descriptionShort: Destruction simulator: physics sandbox, realistic demolition simulation

appDetails.recentChangesHtml: - Game balance changes (first levels are easier)
